Package: SoupLadle
Title: SNP-based patient assignment for pooled scRNA-seq data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Tore Bleckwehl", "Developer", role = c("aut", "cre"), email="tbleckwehl@ukaachen.de",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Based on bulk SNP sequencing data, SoupLadle support the evaluation of the SNP profiles to evaluate the pooling of patients in a large cohort of snRNA-seq studies. Based on the bulk profit, SoupLadle assigns the mixed patients of a snRNA-seq run to the individual patients and marks doublets.
